DEFINITIONS

"Project" means the PRISM codebase, documentation, configuration,
and all files contained in this repository.

"Owner" means the copyright holder identified above.

"Contributor" means any person who submits a pull request to this
repository that is accepted and merged by the Owner.

"Character Identity" means Calista's name, personality design,
speech patterns, lore, visual style, emotional arc, and the
distinctive character feel documented in IDENTITY.md and the
associated system prompt files.

